"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"In her decision last week on the Epic vs Apple case, Judge Yvonne Gonzalez Rogers wrote this:\\n\\n![](https://avc.com/content/uploads/2021/09/Screen-Shot-2021-09-13-at-6.30.50-AM.png)\\n\\nI am not a lawyer, but I read that to say that apps that use crypto rails for payments cannot be blocked by Apple anymore.\\n\\nIf so, that is a decision of enormous consequences for the crypto sector and yet another opening for it.\\n\\nThat is so fucking awesome.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1631529354,\"title\":\"The Apple Epic Decision Is A Breakthrough For Crypto\",\"publication\":\"avc\"},\"digest\":\"AbVtXZCBEoYJATDfv17h0va-srRQcoJrzqNycAm_8bY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xB8332710AB60A1B2e8FE6D775d83524C9E0cE136\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"LTl3aLSRol2QUVUD6CZDmgOh-_8_repOG-vj-b00m1o\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Q21DlwnMAzKTxzvSjREQR-eWtchCVIOEf9pQ8-_jbbs\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"egyU0-rrxQqKqcOODqNNssxOn-cOtAHi7QI_1F-JPq_a3OMaFsKTvo-qza6nQ4pYN3bZrDw9PSzSAH0PEeJ0Qg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xa36ed4a1f484cc32e85a01be266ff07df93d7d551959ab6f44e5cb7aca49bba22841e81a419ff9150996b75ecf4a0a87eda7e1e79898e4f8e48a13744383f7451b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on avc.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"LTl3aLSRol2QUVUD6CZDmgOh-_8_repOG-vj-b00m1o\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Q21DlwnMAzKTxzvSjREQR-eWtchCVIOEf9pQ8-_jbbs\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"AbVtXZCBEoYJATDfv17h0va-srRQcoJrzqNycAm_8bY\"}"